# 20 – NEXUS Workspace AI Rules

- Require macOS ≥ 12, Apple **M3**, and triple-display aware layouts.
- Core deps: `yabai`, `skhd`, Python 3.9, optional `n8n`, BetterTouchTool, Keyboard Maestro.
- Use MLX/transformers stacks stored at `/Volumes/MICRO/models` or `/Volumes/MICRO/LM_STUDIO_MODELS`.
- Quickstart must cover: start yabai service, run `./launcher.sh`, load workspace profiles, open dashboard.
- Provide per-profile model recommendations (work/pessoal/AI research) favoring MLX/GGUF builds.
- Enforce privacy-first local processing; include Streamlit dashboard commands when user requests UI.

